{"word":"H680 - אָצַל - ʼâtsal - aw-tsal' - Keep","slug":"H680","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָצַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼâtsal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-tsal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Keep"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05E6;&#x05DC; - 'a&#x0302;tsal</b> - <i>aw-tsal'<p/></i>A primitive root; properly to <i>join</i>; used only as a denominative from <a href=\"#/H681\">H681</a>; to <i>separate</i>; hence to <i>select, refuse, contract</i>: - keep, reserve, straiten, take."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1018\">H1018</a>, <a href=\"#/H678\">H678</a>, <a href=\"#/H679\">H679</a>, <a href=\"#/H681\">H681</a>, <a href=\"#/H682\">H682</a>, <a href=\"#/H683\">H683</a>"}]}